          <p>(Code 1933, ยง 41A-2602, enacted by Ga. L. 1974, p. 705, ยง 1; Ga. L. 2021, p. 323, ยง 20/HB 111.)</p>
          <p>The 2021 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2021, substituted "prescribed by Code Section 7-1-532" for "prescribed by subsection (c) of Code Section 7-1-552" at the end of paragraph (6).</p>
